(507,	3,	'2025-05-21 07:00:35',	'2025-05-21 07:00:35',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This section provides an overview of the main software applications currently used at Scuola Normale Superiore to support academic, administrative and technical operations. The listed platforms cover a wide range of functions: student career management, financial and accounting systems, resource planning, facility and asset management, internal communication, digital learning tools, and more.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Each application is presented with a brief description highlighting its purpose, target users, access methods, and available support channels. The aim is to guide staff, faculty and students in identifying the digital tools most relevant to their operational needs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Applications and Platforms',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'applications-and-platforms',	'',	'',	'2025-05-21 07:00:36',	'2025-05-21 07:00:36',	'',	0,	'https://demoict.local/?post_type=dis-service-cluster&#038;p=507',	0,	'dis-service-cluster',	'',	0),
(510,	3,	'2025-05-21 07:16:30',	'2025-05-21 07:16:30',	'<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"\"} -->\n<p><strong>Agenda web</strong> √® il servizio online per la consultazione dell‚Äôorario delle lezioni e degli eventi didattici offerto dalla Scuola, basato sulla piattaforma <em>Agenda Web</em> di Easy Academy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"\"} -->\n<p>Il sistema consente a studenti, docenti e personale accademico di accedere in modo semplice, centralizzato e aggiornato agli orari delle attivit√† formative, con indicazione di sedi, aule, docenti e eventuali variazioni. I calendari sono organizzati per corso di studio, insegnamento o docente, e possono essere filtrati e personalizzati in base alle preferenze dell‚Äôutente.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"\"} -->\n<p>Il servizio supporta inoltre la visualizzazione da dispositivi mobili, la generazione di orari personalizzati e l‚Äôesportazione in formato digitale (PDF, ICS). √à pensato per migliorare l‚Äôorganizzazione individuale e semplificare l‚Äôaccesso alle informazioni didattiche in tempo reale.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"\"} -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Agenda web per studenti e docenti',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'agenda-web-per-studenti-e-docenti',	'',	'',	'2025-08-04 12:39:43',	'2025-08-04 12:39:43',	'',	0,	'https://demoict.local/?post_type=dis-service&#038;p=510',	0,	'dis-service',	'',	0),
(519,	3,	'2025-05-21 07:37:48',	'2025-05-21 07:37:48',	'<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"\"} -->\n<p><strong>Agenda Web</strong> is the online service for viewing class schedules and academic events at Scuola  powered by the <em>Agenda Web</em> platform developed by Easy Academy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"\"} -->\n<p>The system allows students, lecturers and academic staff to access up-to-date information about teaching activities, including times, locations, instructors and any changes. Timetables can be viewed by study program, course or teacher, and customized using intuitive filters.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"\"} -->\n<p>The service supports mobile access, personalized schedule generation, and export in digital formats (PDF, ICS). It is designed to improve personal planning and ensure easy access to real-time academic scheduling.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Agenda Web for students and faculty',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'agenda-web-for-students-and-faculty',	'',	'',	'2025-08-04 12:39:23',	'2025-08-04 12:39:23',	'',	0,	'https://demoict.local/?post_type=dis-service&#038;p=519',	0,	'dis-service',	'',	0),
